meta.description:
You get a well-researched comprehensive list and description of your state 
and federal laws that protect you from discrimination.

You also get the name and address of the state agency that handles civil 
rights complaints in your state.

Plus, additional laws that protect you from being discriminated against, 
false imprisonment, false charges of arrest and more!

Instant .pdf download.

(Link expires 24 hours after first download, so save it to your computer.)

These laws are to educate you, your loved ones and businesses. We ask that 
you do not embed on any website without written permission. Thank you for 
your support.

title: NEW JERSEY State and Federal Laws — THE HEALTHY AMERICAN.org
